### Payment Reporting:
Payment reports follow the same principle. They provide payment event line items with a snapshot of the payment state at each stage of its lifecycle.
This model is also consistent with the {% link title="Payment Updated webhook payload" href="/api-reference/webhook-topics/payment-updated/" /%}.

1. **Payment Report Line Item:**
